00:49:36.620 --> 00:49:43.270
But it only, plagiarism only
extends in many cases as far

00:49:43.270 --> 00:49:56.670
as norms allow and today we have
contracts will usually negate

00:49:56.670 --> 00:50:02.420
some of what we would consider
plagiarism or violation

